What does the following error message tell you:

NameError: undefined local variable or method `shoes' for main:Object
  from (irb):3
  from /usr/local/rvm/rubies/ruby-2.0.0-rc2/bin/irb:16:in `<main>'

The error line 3 of irb
No local varible or method defined for 'shoes',
meaning that the shoes variable/ method doesn't exist,
or is outside the scope in which it is being used.